place_name: So Much More To The Story: A Bookery

details.place_name: So Much More To The Story Bookery
details.description: We are a book store that specializes in new books and new releases. We have prepared a selection of books and related items that have been specially chosen and organized for you. Whether you are looking for yourself or a gift for a friend or family member, we have some special options for you. We are happy to recommend some things we love and hope that you love them too!

reviews_data.review_text: This is a wonderful bookstore! I was so happy with the variety of selections and how neat the store was. The customer service was great, and I loved how I got a very deal. I  bought 4 books on (8/22), and a bookmark! You will save so much money here than ordering from Amazon,  Barnes and Nobles  and etc! The perk is that you can request a book and have them order for you! 💓💓💓💓💓💓❤️
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for your kind review! We love to hear that you had such a great experience and hope to see you again soon. Thank you for supporting us. It means so much to us!

reviews_data.review_text: Wonderful place to go!  My granddaughter loved that they had a variety of story books her age for going back to school!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you Shannon! Hope that you and your granddaughter had the best day shopping with us. Come see us again for our fall and Halloween books.

reviews_data.review_text: I went to the bookstore yesterday and I had a phenomenal experience l! Both of the workers at the register were so sweet and welcoming! Definitely will be coming back & huge props to the kind employees!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you! That means a lot. Hope to see you soon.

reviews_data.review_text: My boyfriend and I came across this shop and we thought it was cute so we decided to walk in and the two ladies behind the counter could of been teenagers or early 20’s just stared at us and didn’t even greet us or anything. I brushed it off and continue looking & as I got closer they were both on their phones just laughing and not even paying attention to their customers. I’ve been to many book stores and I never been to one that was so unwelcoming like this one. Cute store, but greeting customers is not a hard thing to do.
reviews_data.owner_answer: I am so disheartened to read this review and truly apologize! We pride ourselves on customer experience. We always appreciate people coming in to shop our small business. We are honored when people spend their time and money to shop with us instead of Amazon or other big retailers. I’m very sorry you had a poor experience.

reviews_data.review_text: What an absolutely adorable bookstore! I just happened by as I was in downtown Monroe and it truly took my breath away. It looked like something out of a TV show or movie. You should check it out!
reviews_data.owner_answer: So kind! Thank you for coming in. Hope to see you again soon.

reviews_data.review_text: Adorable shop in downtown Monroe! I was happy with the book selection and loved that they had kids books as well as book and reader related gifts like stickers, journals, bookmarks, candles and some apparel.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much for coming to shop with us! And thank you for your kind words. Hope to see you again soon.

reviews_data.review_text: Adorable bookstore that carries the most recent and trending books. A great addition to the downtown Monroe area!
reviews_data.owner_answer: 🩵 Thank you! We love being a part of this community.

reviews_data.review_text: cutest bookstore i’ve ever been to. good selection too!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much! We are so glad you took the time to come in and to leave such a nice review.

reviews_data.review_text: I am participating in the greater Charlotte book crawll, this is my first visit to the store. It is very cute and spacious. There's a lot of bookish things. From the sections I've seen, their main focus is children's books, fantasy books, rom-coms, mystery thriller and Young adult (middle grade). I asked the lady at the front desk what is the process for local authors to have their books in their bookstore and you must email the owner and you will discuss the process in where to go from there.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Dana, thank you for coming to see us.  We do have local author books! We have a form to fill out for indie authors that will be emailed to you.  Our shop is small, but we try to have something for everyone. Thanks for coming to see us and we hope to see you again.

reviews_data.review_text: Awesome bookstore. Quaint and cute with so much to offer. Located in the heart of Monroe NC. Give them a visit!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for your kind review! So glad you took the time to come visit.

reviews_data.review_text: Stopped in out of curiosity and was pleasantly surprised. As another reviewer stated there is an overall vibe of cozy genre, young adult reads, classics and a wonderful assortment of elementary level book series. My teenagers were voracious readers until about 13 and I often hear their frustration in finding books that truly engage them. From my impression today I am hopeful this is a place that will have a wide variety of recommendations for this 13-18 age group to find engaging age appropriate novels that aren't TOO mature. A good selection of thoughtful gifts for all ages. Appreciated that it wasn't packed with too much inventory...there is space to breathe and feel calm as opposed to that overstimulated feeling common to many boutiques. I look forward to visiting again and hope to see frequent changes to gifts and books curated to the seasons/holidays.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you! This review means so much to us! Thank you for your kind words. We do put so much thought into our inventory and our space. Thank you for coming in, and we hope to see you again sometime.

reviews_data.review_text:
What a blessing it is to finally have a bookstore in downtown Monroe!
This sweet little shop is such a pleasant experience and aesthetically pleasing to the eye. The atmosphere is warm and inviting, so calm and peaceful that you want to curl up and read your book right there!
The owners are welcoming and kind, they have truly created something very special.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much!!! We appreciate the support and kind words. We are so grateful to be a part of this community.

reviews_data.review_text: Soooo cute!! I happened to be in Monroe and stopped by and was so impressed. Lots of genres and really cute displays and gifts.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you! So glad you stopped in and hope you come back soon.

reviews_data.review_text: What a sweet bookstore! It leans into more of what I think of as cozy reads as well as books for younger readers. Loved the selection of gifts and the comfy vibes. Loved the nice paper bag and bookmark that came with my purchase.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for coming in Jessie!

reviews_data.review_text: Charming shop with an awesome selection of books—popular titles and new releases as well as great editions of classics and backlist titles. I saw multiple editions here that I had only ever found online and had been curious to see in person before buying. They also had a wide selection of gifts and great children’s books too!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you! So glad you come in! Thank you for your kind words and support.

reviews_data.review_text: I love this bookstore! Everyone is so friendly and helpful. Highly recommend
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks, Grace! This made us so happy!

reviews_data.review_text: Finally we get a bookstore in Monroe!! I love So much more to the story bookery! They have a good variety of books! It’s so nice driving 5 minutes to a bookstore vs driving to Charlotte to Barnes and noble! The staff is always so kind! Thank you for opening!! I will definitely recommend all my friends and family here! :-)
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks so much! We are so happy to be a part of this community. Thank you for coming in and hope to see you again soon.

reviews_data.review_text: Such an adorable little book store with a nice variety.  The staff, Grace & Emma-Grace (seriously) were welcoming & attentive. Looking forward to visiting them again soon.
reviews_data.owner_answer: So glad that you were able to come and hope we get to see you again soon! Thanks for the kind words. We really appreciate it.

reviews_data.review_text: Beautiful bookstore, beautiful employees. I stopped in here with one of my besties and our kiddos. We also met the owner and thanked her for such a lovely place in Monroe.
reviews_data.owner_answer: So glad we got to meet you! Thank you for your support and coming in.

reviews_data.review_text: I love this bookstore! Decided to pop in to check it out since it’s newer and ended up not wanting to leave. It has such a great selection of books ranging from all genres. It also has a great selection of children’s books. I definitely recommend this gem in Monroe!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you!!! And thank you for coming to see us. Hope you come back again soon.
